# AI Development Rules

## Purpose

Govern how Cursor agents operate in this repository.

## Model Routing

Follow `core/08-model-routing.mdc`:

| Task | Model |
|------|-------|
| Implementation / verification | Composer 2.5 |
| Research / planning / orchestration | GPT-5.5 |
| Architecture / security / payments | Opus (reserved) |

Opus is reserved for `enterprise-architect`, `security-auditor`, `checkout-specialist`
(AI-002). Orchestration and verification default to cheaper models. See
`docs/MODEL-ROUTING.md`.

## Skills

- Load one primary domain skill per task
- Use `skill-router` when unsure
- Native skills: model-routing, context-loading, implement-checkout-flow, implement-catalog-feature, playwright-e2e-checkout

## Subagents

Use `.cursor/agents/` specialists (11 total):

| Agent | Domain |
|-------|--------|
| enterprise-architect | Architecture, ADRs |
| backend-engineer | FastAPI features |
| frontend-engineer | Next.js, shadcn |
| database-engineer | PostgreSQL, migrations |
| api-engineer | OpenAPI, REST |
| catalog-specialist | Product catalog |
| checkout-specialist | Checkout, Stripe |
| security-auditor | Security, PCI (readonly) |
| qa-engineer | E2E, Playwright |
| devops-engineer | Docker, CI |
| verifier | Validation (readonly) |

Use `subagent-orchestrator` for 3+ file parallel work.

## Context Budget

- Max 4 always-on rules: `core/00-core`, `01-project`, `02-ai-behavior`, `10-project-state-management`
- Load domain rules via globs only
- Enable MCP servers on demand only

## Project State

Before any task, read `.cursor/project-management/` per `core/10-project-state-management.mdc` and skill `context-loading`.

After any session, update `PROJECT_STATUS.md`, `TASKS.md`, `HANDOFF.md`, and `CURRENT_CONTEXT.md`.

## Memory MCP

Before new conventions or patterns, check Memory MCP for existing decisions. Memory MCP stores conventions — not task tracking (use `TASKS.md`).

## Anti-Patterns

- Using Opus for CRUD boilerplate
- Running per-feature orchestration or verification on Opus (use GPT-5.5 / Composer 2.5)
- Loading all 46 skills at once
- Ignoring architecture rules for "speed"
- Skipping verifier on payment features

